data.description: You have an opportunity for a like-new house built in 2022. This 5-bedroom triple bathroom house is barely a year old and on the market for sale. The house is protected by a gated community and efficiently powered by solar panels (fully paid). The house includes the luxury package upgrade from the builder. The quiet neighborhood is perfect for raising a family. For the outdoor enthusiast, Sequoia National Park and Kings Canyon National Park are driving distance from the house. Experience the four seasons at the surrounding national parks! The house is ready to become your next home.
